330
00:26:23,916 --> 00:26:25,709
-Mahal! honey!
-Nanay!

331
00:26:25,793 --> 00:26:28,045
-Ma'am! Gumising ka na ma'am!
-Mahal!

332
00:26:28,128 --> 00:26:30,422
-Mahal!
-Ma'am!

333
00:26:30,964 --> 00:26:33,133
-Ma'am! Oh, mahal na kabutihan!
-Nay, gising na!

334
00:26:33,217 --> 00:26:35,719
Simula noong araw na iniwan ka ng nanay mo…

335
00:26:35,803 --> 00:26:37,096
